The patch PESEdit Patch 2014 v1.3 adds the English second division. In the championship Sky Bet Championship included 18 teams with all the right forms , faces , trains , etc. Also, updated forms for some teams , and added new football boots from Adidas Samba Pack.
PESEdit Patch 2014 v1.3 also includes a program FileLoader facilitates installation of different mods.
